          </table></p><p>The change in the resource element of the DEL arises from the draw down of &#x00A3;78,102,000 administration costs EYF, and additional income for VOA services.</p><p>The change in the capital element of the DEL arises from the draw down of capital EYF and non-discretionary EYF, totalling &#x00A3;37,631,000 as set out in the Public expenditure Outturn White Paper (CM5574). It also includes the draw down of &#x00A3;900,000 from the Capital Modernisation Fund.</p><p><table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Resources (&#x00A3;) Change</span></td>
